These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
Beverage: cola, hot-chocolate, mirinda, tea
Job: photographer, firefighter, fisherman, designer
1. Beverage:hot-chocolate is between Beverage:cola and Job:firefighter##2
2. Beverage:hot-chocolate is on the left or right of Job:photographer##3
3. Beverage:hot-chocolate is somewhere between Beverage:tea and Beverage:cola##7
4. Job:firefighter is in an even position##4
5. Beverage:tea is on the right of Job:fisherman##1
6. Job:firefighter is somewhere to the left of Job:photographer##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | mirinda | tea       | hot-chocolate | cola        |
| Job      | fisherman  | firefighter | designer        | photographer |

