.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-2::.
House: craftsman, art-deco, modern, tower
Sport: cycling, rowing, skateboarding, volleyball
1. Sport:volleyball is somewhere between Sport:skateboarding and House:modern##7
2. House:tower is somewhere to the left of House:craftsman##5
3. House:tower is somewhere to the right of Sport:volleyball##5
4. House:art-deco is on the left of House:tower##1
5. Sport:volleyball is between Sport:skateboarding and Sport:rowing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| House     | modern | art-deco       | tower         | craftsman     |
| Sport   | rowing   | volleyball | skateboarding | cycling |

