2. Hobby:collecting is somewhere between Nationality:nigerian and Hobby:writing##7
3. Hobby:woodworking == Nationality:turkish##1
4. Nationality:malaysian is on the left of Nationality:turkish##1
5. Hobby:traveling is on the left of Nationality:japanese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |      4      |
| Hobby   | traveling | collecting | writing       | woodworking |
| Nationality   | nigerian      | japanese   | malaysian | turkish  |

